Angular features

1.Component (root-AppComponent)

2.Module(root-AppModule)

3.Data binding

    3.1 one way binding(Data flows from component to view and view to component)

    (A):component to view
        String Interpolation/Interpolation ({{expression}})
        property binding - [Binding-target]="Binding source"

    (B):view to component   

        Event binding:(event)="function call"
        Event binding using dollar event ($)event (event)="function call"

        Template referencing variable (#)


3.2 Two way binding
    (A) ngModel is defined in (FormsModules/)
    syntax:
    [(ngModel)="variable name"]

    Dependency injection